<div class="section">
    <form class="service-form">
        <h3>무료 방문상담 신청</h3>
        <div class="description">
            <span class="required">*</span>
            <span>로 표시된 항목은 필수 입력항목입니다.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <span class="required">*</span>
                <span class="number">1</span>
                <span class="value">성함</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">고객님의 성함을 입력해주세요.</div>
            <input type="text" name="user_name" id="user_name" placeholder="홍길동">
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <!--
                <span class="required">*</span>
                -->
                <span class="number">2</span>
                <span class="value">가족구성원</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">고객님의 가족구성원을 선택해주세요.</div>
            <select name="user_family" id="user_family" class="selectric">
                <option value="">가족구성원 선택</option>
                <option value="싱글라이프">싱글라이프</option>
                <option value="신혼부부">신혼부부</option>
                <option value="초등학교 입학전의 아이를 둔 부부">초등학교 입학전의 아이를 둔 부부</option>
                <option value="어머니 아버지를 모시고 사는 20~30대">어머니 아버지를 모시고 사는 20~30대</option>
                <option value="시어머니 시아버지 등을 모시고 사는 결혼한 부부">시어머니 시아버지 등을 모시고 사는 결혼한 부부</option>
                <option value="시어머니 시아버지 등을 모시고 사는 결혼한 부부 + 아이를 둔 부부">시어머니 시아버지 등을 모시고 사는 결혼한 부부 + 아이를 둔 부부</option>
                <option value="other">기타</option>
            </select>
            <input type="text" name="user_family_other" id="user_family_other" class="none" placeholder="가족구성원을 입력해주세요">
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <!--
                <span class="required">*</span>
                -->
                <span class="number">3</span>
                <span class="value">평수</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">고객님이 예상하는 평수를 선택해주세요.</div>
            <select name="user_size" id="user_size" class="selectric">
                <option value="">평수 선택</option>
                <option value="lt20">20평대 미만</option>
                <option value="eq20">20평대</option>
                <option value="eq30">30평대</option>
                <option value="eq40">40평대</option>
                <option value="eq50">50평대</option>
                <option value="eq60">60평대</option>
                <option value="gte70">70평대 이상</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <!--
                <span class="required">*</span>
                -->
                <span class="number">4</span>
                <span class="value">예산</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">고객님이 예상하시는 예산을 입력해주세요.</div>
            <select name="user_budget" id="user_budget" class="selectric">
                <option class="default" value="">예산 선택</option>
                <option value="">먼저 평수를 선택해주세요.</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <!--
                <span class="required">*</span>
                -->
                <span class="number">5</span>
                <span class="value">주소</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">지금 고객님이 인테리어 하실 곳의 주소를 입력해주세요</div>
            <input type="text" name="user_address_brief" id="user_address_brief" placeholder="기본주소 선택 (클릭 시 주소검색 창 열림)">
            <input type="text" name="user_address_detail" id="user_address_detail" placeholder="상세주소 입력">
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <span class="required">*</span>
                <span class="number">6</span>
                <span class="value">연락처</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">고객님의 연락처를 입력해주세요.</div>
            <input type="text" name="user_phone" id="user_phone" class="phone">
            <button class="btn primary auth-request">인증번호요청</button>
        </div>
        <div class="form-item auth" style="display: none">
            <div class="title">
                <span class="required">*</span>
                <span class="value">인증번호</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">인증번호를 입력해주세요.</div>
            <input type="text" name="auth_key" id="auth_key" class="authkey">

            <button class="btn primary auth-validate">인증번호확인</button>
            <span class="auth-timer"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
            <div class="title">
                <!--
                <span class="required">*</span>
                -->
                <span class="number">7</span>
                <span class="value">이사날짜</span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-description">고객님의 이사날짜를 선택해주세요.</div>
            <input type="text" class="calendar" name="user_move_date" id="user_move_date" data-today="<%=moment().add(1, 'days').format('YYYY-MM-DD')%>"
                data-min="<%=moment().add(1, 'days').format('YYYY-MM-DD')%>" placeholder="날짜선택">
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-fold">
            <i></i>
            <span>추가 정보 입력</span>
        </a>
        <div class="form-fold">
            <div class="form-item">
                <div class="title">
                    <span class="number">8</span>
                    <span class="value">인테리어 스타일</span>
                </div>
                <div class="form-description">고객님이 원하시는 스타일을 선택해주세요. (여러 항목 중복 선택가능)</div>
                <input type="hidden" name="user_style_likes" id="user_style_likes">
                <input type="hidden" name="user_style_dislikes" id="user_style_dislikes">
                <div class="form-grid form-grid-zoom form-style">
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="1">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-01.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="2">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-02.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="3">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-03.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="4">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-04.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="5">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-05.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="6">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-06.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="7">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-07.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="8">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-08.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="9">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-image: url('/images/temporary/bg-style-09.jpeg');">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-item">
                <div class="title">
                    <span class="number">9</span>
                    <span class="value">색감</span>
                </div>
                <div class="form-description">고객님이 원하시는 색상을 선택해주세요. (여러 항목 중복 선택가능)</div>
                <input type="hidden" name="user_color_likes" id="user_color_likes">
                <input type="hidden" name="user_color_dislikes" id="user_color_dislikes">
                <div class="form-grid form-color">
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="1">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-color: #f9f2f1;">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn-dislike"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-col" data-value="2">
                        <div class="picture" style="background-color: #0A0200;">
                            <a href="#" class="btn-like"></a>
